Zw","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"56","text":"4. Características\\Nde las lesiones:","guid":"Kc4LTmhHDIMU9LOiRpnJdg","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"- Múltiples angiodisplasias: 40-60% de pacientes [5,9]","guid":"VYekslRCwf8g5bC7IYYnbQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"- Distribución:","guid":"RhvaO1fn6UUROrI_Q52tSA","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• Misma porción del TGI: Mayoría","guid":"DQZxc3L_LX4XD3NFQz2Rog","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"• Lesiones sincrónicas en otras partes del TGI: ~20% [10]","guid":"BajIlUpqEodKyVXBF70H7w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"56","text":"5. Angiodisplasias de\\Nintestino delgado:","guid":"DUGfTxmwdCtNF5awU45xrw","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"- En pacientes con sangrado por angiodisplasia colónica: 23% [10]","guid":"E91AtinDJBY9NER9U5aYPQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"- Detección:","guid":"WzNZH01H5MRft8ylBQFkbg","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• Laparotomía","guid":"NY7xR3SsgEdLmy3kCxaV-Q","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"• Investigación por sangrado recurrente","guid":"SO9CRmyA3p8snL1nDwscgg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"56","text":"6. Consideración\\Nimportante:","guid":"RGjH5T3Xb6ZSqMnKUW85WA","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"→ Angiodisplasia como fuente\\Nde pérdida sanguínea GI:","guid":"MNadJGm4PRAUrMr7Nn9luQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Solo si se observa\\Nsangrado activo","guid":"NCJPl192ILxOPG2oQWPu5g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"Condiciones asociadas a\\Nangiodisplasias:","guid":"Ml3gV2NMKWVFzKnMEnoLbQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"1. Poblaciones de\\N↑ prevalencia:","guid":"H26J10BSOoAlS-X8VP17Hg","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Edad avanzada","guid":"NP66yHDnE-BgFBEXfe39Dg","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"- Pacientes con sangrado GI","guid":"XWfygAywzn4M-RmQIdC6ZQ","child